#: src/index.md:20
msgid "AI Agent Assembly is a governance layer for AI agents. It sits between your agents and the outside world and does three things:"
msgstr "AI Agent Assembly 是 AI 代理的治理層。它位於你的代理與外部世界之間，做三件事："

#: src/index.md:22
msgid "**Enforces policy** — decides, before each action runs, whether an agent is allowed to call a tool, reach a domain, or spend more budget."
msgstr "**強制執行政策** — 在每個動作執行之前，決定代理是否被允許呼叫某個工具、連線某個網域，或動用更多預算。"

#: src/index.md:23
msgid "**Tracks cost** — meters token and dollar spend per team and blocks agents that exceed their budget."
msgstr "**追蹤成本** — 依團隊計量權杖與金額開銷，並封鎖超出預算的代理。"

#: src/index.md:24
msgid "**Intercepts unsafe actions** — catches risky calls (and bypass attempts) at the SDK, network, and kernel levels."
msgstr "**攔截不安全的動作** — 在 SDK、網路與核心層攔截有風險的呼叫（以及繞道嘗試）。"

#: src/index.md:26
msgid "It works across your whole fleet of agents and does not require you to rewrite your existing agent code."
msgstr "它適用於你整個代理機群，且不需要你改寫既有的代理程式碼。"

