#: src/index.md:72
msgid "Prefer learning by running code? The [**agent-assembly-examples**](https://github.com/ai-agent-assembly/examples) repo collects small, framework-specific Agent Assembly examples for Python, Node.js/TypeScript, Go, policy enforcement, approvals, audit, trace, and runtime workflows. Clone it and run an example end to end to see governance in action before instrumenting your own agents."
msgstr "偏好透過執行程式碼來學習嗎？[**agent-assembly-examples**](https://github.com/ai-agent-assembly/examples) 儲存庫收集了針對各框架、精簡的 Agent Assembly 範例，涵蓋 Python、Node.js/TypeScript、Go、政策強制執行、核可、稽核、追蹤與執行期工作流程。將它複製下來，端到端執行一個範例，即可在為你自己的代理裝設檢測之前，實際看見治理的運作。"

#: src/index.md:79
msgid "The three-layer interception model"
msgstr "三層攔截模型"

#: src/index.md:81
msgid "AI Agent Assembly enforces governance through three layers. You can deploy them independently, and each one catches what the layer above it might miss:"
msgstr "AI Agent Assembly 透過三層來強制執行治理。你可以獨立部署各層，且每一層都能捕捉上一層可能遺漏的部分："

#: src/index.md:83
msgid "**SDK layer (in-process)** — the language SDK wraps your agent calls and applies allow/deny decisions before any network request leaves the process. Fastest path, but requires you to adopt the SDK."
msgstr "**SDK 層（行程內）** — 對應語言的 SDK 會包裝你的代理呼叫，並在任何網路請求離開行程之前套用允許／拒絕的決策。這是最快的路徑，但需要你採用該 SDK。"

#: src/index.md:84
msgid "**Sidecar proxy (`aa-proxy`)** — intercepts outbound HTTPS using a per-host CA, so it can govern agents that do not use the SDK. No code changes required."
msgstr "**邊車代理（`aa-proxy`）** — 使用每主機的憑證機構（CA）攔截對外的 HTTPS，因此能治理未使用 SDK 的代理。無需變更程式碼。"

#: src/index.md:85
msgid "**eBPF sensor (`aa-ebpf`)** — kernel-level hooks that watch SSL libraries and process syscalls to catch bypass attempts at the OS level. Linux only."
msgstr "**eBPF 感測器（`aa-ebpf`）** — 核心層級的掛鉤，監看 SSL 函式庫與行程系統呼叫，在作業系統層級捕捉繞道嘗試。僅限 Linux。"

#: src/index.md:87
msgid "All three layers report to the **gateway**, which evaluates policy and tracks per-team budgets."
msgstr "這三層全都回報給**閘道（gateway）**，由閘道評估政策並依團隊追蹤預算。"

#: src/index.md:89
msgid "These three interception points describe _where_ enforcement happens; they sit inside the **Boundary** layer of the broader [five-layer defense model](security-model.md), which describes _what_ is protected. Same system, two views."
msgstr "這三個攔截點描述的是強制執行發生的_位置_；它們位於更廣泛的[五層防禦模型](security-model.md)中的 **Boundary** 層內，而該模型描述的是_受保護的對象_。同一套系統，兩種視角。"

