#: src/faq.md:1
msgid "FAQ"
msgstr "常見問題（FAQ）"

#: src/faq.md:3
msgid "Answers to the questions first-time visitors ask before reading any of the detailed pages. Each answer links to where the topic is covered in full."
msgstr "回答初次到訪者在閱讀任何詳細頁面之前會提出的問題。每則回答都連結到完整說明該主題之處。"

#: src/faq.md:6
msgid "What is AI Agent Assembly, in one sentence?"
msgstr "用一句話說，AI Agent Assembly 是什麼？"

#: src/faq.md:8
msgid "It is a **governance layer for AI agents**: it sits between your agents and the outside world and enforces policy, tracks cost, and intercepts unsafe actions _before_ they run. See the [Introduction](README.md) and [Why AI Agent Assembly?](comparison.md)."
msgstr "它是 **AI 代理的治理層**：位於你的代理與外部世界之間，在不安全的動作執行_之前_，強制執行政策、追蹤成本並加以攔截。請參閱[簡介](README.md)與[為何選擇 AI Agent Assembly？](comparison.md)。"

#: src/faq.md:13
msgid "Do I have to change my agent's code?"
msgstr "我必須修改代理的程式碼嗎？"

#: src/faq.md:15
msgid "Not necessarily. There are three interception layers and you can pick how invasive to be:"
msgstr "不一定。共有三層攔截，你可以自行選擇侵入程度："

#: src/faq.md:18
msgid "The **SDK layer** needs a small amount of instrumentation in your code and is the fastest path."
msgstr "**SDK 層**需要在你的程式碼中加入少量檢測，是最快的路徑。"

#: src/faq.md:20
msgid "The **sidecar proxy** (`aa-proxy`) governs an agent's network traffic with **no code change**."
msgstr "**邊車代理**（`aa-proxy`）治理代理的網路流量，**無需變更程式碼**。"

#: src/faq.md:22
msgid "The **eBPF sensor** (`aa-ebpf`, Linux only) catches actions at the kernel level, including bypass attempts."
msgstr "**eBPF 感測器**（`aa-ebpf`，僅限 Linux）在核心層級捕捉動作，包含繞道嘗試。"

#: src/faq.md:25
msgid "See the three-layer interception model in the [Introduction](README.md)."
msgstr "請參閱[簡介](README.md)中的三層攔截模型。"

#: src/faq.md:27
msgid "Does it work with my LLM / framework?"
msgstr "它能搭配我的 LLM／框架運作嗎？"

#: src/faq.md:29
msgid "Yes — it is provider-agnostic. It governs agents regardless of which model provider you use, and ships SDKs for **Python, TypeScript/Node, and Go**, with framework examples (LangChain, LlamaIndex, bare OpenAI, and more) in the [examples repository](https://github.com/ai-agent-assembly/examples)."
msgstr "可以 — 它與供應商無關。無論你使用哪家模型供應商，它都能治理代理，並提供 **Python、TypeScript/Node 與 Go** 的 SDK，且在[範例儲存庫](https://github.com/ai-agent-assembly/examples)中附有各框架範例（LangChain、LlamaIndex、純 OpenAI 等）。"

#: src/faq.md:34
msgid "Is it free? What is open source vs. paid?"
msgstr "它免費嗎？哪些是開源、哪些是付費？"

#: src/faq.md:36
msgid "The enforcement core — the interception layers, policy engine, SDKs, and CLI — is **open source under Apache-2.0**. Enterprise operations (SSO, SCIM, tamper-evident audit, dedicated regions, SLAs) are commercial and delivered on paid SaaS tiers. See the [Open core boundary](open-core-boundary.md)."
msgstr "強制執行的核心 — 攔截層、政策引擎、各 SDK 與 CLI — 是**採 Apache-2.0 授權的開源**。企業級維運（SSO、SCIM、防竄改稽核、專屬地區、SLA）屬商業功能，透過付費 SaaS 方案提供。請參閱[開放核心邊界](open-core-boundary.md)。"

#: src/faq.md:41
msgid "Can I self-host it?"
msgstr "我可以自行託管嗎？"

#: src/faq.md:43
msgid "You can self-host a **limited-function** stack from the open-source crates (using the published Docker Compose example) for local evaluation and development. The **complete** feature set is delivered through the AI Agent Assembly cloud (SaaS). See the [Open core boundary](open-core-boundary.md)."
msgstr "你可以從開源 crates 自行託管一套**功能受限**的堆疊（使用已發布的 Docker Compose 範例），供本地評估與開發之用。**完整**的功能集則透過 AI Agent Assembly 雲端（SaaS）提供。請參閱[開放核心邊界](open-core-boundary.md)。"

#: src/faq.md:48
msgid "How does it actually block an unsafe action?"
msgstr "它實際上如何封鎖不安全的動作？"

#: src/faq.md:50
msgid "Before an agent action runs, the gateway evaluates your policy and returns an allow or deny decision; a deny stops the action. Budgets are enforced the same way — once a team is over budget, further calls are denied. See the [Policy reference](policy-reference.md)."
msgstr "在代理動作執行之前，閘道會評估你的政策並回傳允許或拒絕的決策；拒絕會停止該動作。預算也以相同方式強制執行 — 一旦團隊超出預算，後續呼叫即被拒絕。請參閱[政策參考](policy-reference.md)。"

#: src/faq.md:55
msgid "How is it different from an observability / tracing tool?"
msgstr "它與可觀測性／追蹤工具有何不同？"

#: src/faq.md:57
msgid "Observability tools record what an agent _did_, after the fact. AI Agent Assembly makes a binding **allow/deny decision before the action executes**. The [comparison page](comparison.md) maps this against other tools."
msgstr "可觀測性工具是在事後記錄代理_做過_什麼。AI Agent Assembly 則在**動作執行之前做出具約束力的允許／拒絕決策**。[比較頁面](comparison.md)將此與其他工具對照。"

#: src/faq.md:61
msgid "Where do I get started right now?"
msgstr "我現在該從哪裡開始？"

#: src/faq.md:63
msgid "Clone the [examples repository](https://github.com/ai-agent-assembly/examples) and run a governed agent end to end — that is the path you can run today. The managed [Quick start (SaaS)](quickstart-saas.md) is coming soon."
msgstr "複製[範例儲存庫](https://github.com/ai-agent-assembly/examples)並端到端執行一個受治理的代理 — 這是你今天就能執行的路徑。託管式的[快速開始（SaaS）](quickstart-saas.md)即將推出。"

#: src/faq.md:67
msgid "What do the acronyms mean (eBPF, SCIM, mTLS, STRIDE…)?"
msgstr "這些縮寫是什麼意思（eBPF、SCIM、mTLS、STRIDE…）？"

#: src/faq.md:69
msgid "See the [Glossary](glossary.md), which defines every recurring term and acronym in plain language."
msgstr "請參閱[詞彙表](glossary.md)，其中以淺白語言定義每個反覆出現的術語與縮寫。"

