#: src/comparison.md:80
msgid "**Immutable tamper-evident audit log** — AAASM's audit log entries are signed with HMAC-SHA256, making post-hoc alteration detectable. This is a compliance requirement in regulated industries (PCI-DSS, SOC 2 Type II) that no competitor in this matrix fully addresses."
msgstr ""

