#: src/quickstart-saas.md:9
msgid "**Full functionality is SaaS.** A limited-function stack is self-hostable from the Apache-2.0 crates for local evaluation and development; complete governance, policy evaluation, and audit logging at production grade run in the AI Agent Assembly cloud. See [Open core boundary](open-core-boundary.md) for the licensing model."
msgstr "**完整功能為 SaaS。** 可從 Apache-2.0 crates 自行託管一套功能受限的堆疊，供本地評估與開發；正式環境等級的完整治理、政策評估與稽核紀錄則在 AI Agent Assembly 雲端執行。授權模式請參閱[開放核心邊界](open-core-boundary.md)。"

