#: src/quickstart-saas.md:86
msgid "The `init_assembly` session plus the wired callback handler do three things, without touching LangChain internals:"
msgstr "`init_assembly` 工作階段搭配已接線的 callback handler，在不觸及 LangChain 內部的情況下完成三件事："

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:88
msgid "Register `langchain-research-agent` with the gateway."
msgstr "向閘道註冊 `langchain-research-agent`。"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:89
msgid "Run a policy check before each tool/LLM call, blocking it if policy denies."
msgstr "在每次工具／LLM 呼叫之前執行政策檢查，若政策拒絕則加以封鎖。"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:90
msgid "Emit an audit event for every call."
msgstr "為每次呼叫發出一則稽核事件。"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:92
msgid "**Deny is enforced — a blocked call raises.** With the idiomatic `callbacks=[handler]` wiring shown above, a policy **deny** stops the tool/LLM call by **raising an exception** that propagates out of `executor.invoke(...)`; the denied action does not run. (The deny is no longer swallowed — wrap the `invoke` call in `try`/`except` if you want to handle a blocked action gracefully instead of letting it surface.)"
msgstr "**拒絕會被強制執行 — 被封鎖的呼叫會拋出例外。** 採用上方慣用的 `callbacks=[handler]` 接線方式時，政策**拒絕**會以**拋出例外**的方式停止該工具／LLM 呼叫，該例外會傳播出 `executor.invoke(...)`；被拒絕的動作不會執行。（拒絕不再被吞掉 — 若你想優雅地處理被封鎖的動作而非讓它冒出，請以 `try`/`except` 包住 `invoke` 呼叫。）"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:99
msgid "Step 4 — Activate a starter policy"
msgstr "步驟 4 — 啟用入門政策"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:101
msgid "In the console, open **Policies → New Policy** and apply the starter template (allow all, audit all). This takes under 30 seconds. From now on, every call from `langchain-research-agent` is governed, audited, and visible in the **Audit Log** panel."
msgstr "在主控台中，開啟 **Policies → New Policy** 並套用入門範本（全部允許、全部稽核）。這只需不到 30 秒。從此之後，來自 `langchain-research-agent` 的每次呼叫都會被治理、稽核，並顯示於 **Audit Log** 面板中。"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:103
msgid "What governance looks like at runtime"
msgstr "治理在執行期的樣貌"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:113
msgid "Pro Tier"
msgstr "Pro 方案"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:115
msgid "**Signup**: planned self-serve at `https://app.agent-assembly.com/signup` — **not yet live** while Cloud is in early access. [Request Cloud early access](https://agent-assembly.com/early-access) to be notified when Pro-tier signup opens."
msgstr "**註冊**：計畫於 `https://app.agent-assembly.com/signup` 提供自助註冊 — 在 Cloud 處於搶先體驗期間**尚未上線**。請[申請 Cloud 搶先體驗](https://agent-assembly.com/early-access)，以便在 Pro 方案註冊開放時收到通知。"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:117
msgid "**Included features**: up to 10 agents, basic policy engine (allow/deny/audit), 30-day audit log retention, community forum support."
msgstr "**內含功能**：最多 10 個代理、基本政策引擎（允許／拒絕／稽核）、30 天稽核紀錄保存、社群論壇支援。"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:119
msgid "**Expected onboarding time**: ~10 minutes from signup to first governed agent call."
msgstr "**預期上手時間**：從註冊到第一次受治理的代理呼叫約 10 分鐘。"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:121
msgid "**Primary contact channel**: self-serve; community forum at `https://community.agent-assembly.com`."
msgstr "**主要聯絡管道**：自助；社群論壇位於 `https://community.agent-assembly.com`。"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:123
msgid "Pro signup steps"
msgstr "Pro 註冊步驟"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:125
msgid "**Coming soon** — once Cloud is generally available, you'll navigate to `https://app.agent-assembly.com/signup` and create an account with your work email. The signup endpoint is not live yet; [request early access](https://agent-assembly.com/early-access) in the meantime."
msgstr "**即將推出** — 待 Cloud 全面上線後，你將前往 `https://app.agent-assembly.com/signup`，以你的工作電子郵件建立帳號。註冊端點尚未上線；在此期間請[申請搶先體驗](https://agent-assembly.com/early-access)。"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:126
msgid "Verify your email address."
msgstr "驗證你的電子郵件地址。"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:127
msgid "On the **Workspace Setup** page, enter a workspace name (e.g., `acme-ai-ops`) and select your primary region."
msgstr "在 **Workspace Setup** 頁面輸入工作區名稱（例如 `acme-ai-ops`）並選擇你的主要地區。"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:128
msgid "Copy your **Workspace ID** and generate an **API Key** under **Settings → API Keys**."
msgstr "複製你的 **Workspace ID**，並在 **Settings → API Keys** 下產生一組 **API Key**。"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:129
msgid "Install the SDK for your language — see the [Python SDK quick start](https://docs.agent-assembly.com/python-sdk/), [Node SDK quick start](https://docs.agent-assembly.com/node-sdk/), or [Go SDK quick start](https://docs.agent-assembly.com/go-sdk/)."
msgstr "安裝對應語言的 SDK — 請參閱 [Python SDK 快速開始](https://docs.agent-assembly.com/python-sdk/)、[Node SDK 快速開始](https://docs.agent-assembly.com/node-sdk/) 或 [Go SDK 快速開始](https://docs.agent-assembly.com/go-sdk/)。"

