#: src/quickstart-saas.md:167
msgid "Business Tier"
msgstr "Business 方案"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:169
msgid "**Signup**: planned self-serve at `https://app.agent-assembly.com/signup` (select **Business** during workspace setup) — **not yet live** while Cloud is in early access. [Request Cloud early access](https://agent-assembly.com/early-access) to be notified when Business-tier signup opens."
msgstr "**註冊**：計畫於 `https://app.agent-assembly.com/signup` 提供自助註冊（在工作區設定時選擇 **Business**）— 在 Cloud 處於搶先體驗期間**尚未上線**。請[申請 Cloud 搶先體驗](https://agent-assembly.com/early-access)，以便在 Business 方案註冊開放時收到通知。"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:171
msgid "**Included features**: up to 50 agents, full policy engine, SSO (SAML 2.0 / OIDC), 90-day audit log retention, SIEM export, business-hours support (24h response)."
msgstr "**內含功能**：最多 50 個代理、完整政策引擎、SSO（SAML 2.0 / OIDC）、90 天稽核紀錄保存、SIEM 匯出、上班時間支援（24 小時內回覆）。"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:173
msgid "**Expected onboarding time**: ~30 minutes, including SSO connect."
msgstr "**預期上手時間**：約 30 分鐘，含 SSO 連接。"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:175
msgid "**Primary contact channel**: support ticket via `https://app.agent-assembly.com/support`."
msgstr "**主要聯絡管道**：透過 `https://app.agent-assembly.com/support` 提交支援工單。"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:177
msgid "Business signup steps"
msgstr "Business 註冊步驟"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:179
msgid "**Coming soon** — once Cloud is generally available, you'll sign up at `https://app.agent-assembly.com/signup` and select the **Business** tier. The signup endpoint is not live yet; [request early access](https://agent-assembly.com/early-access) in the meantime."
msgstr "**即將推出** — 待 Cloud 全面上線後，你將於 `https://app.agent-assembly.com/signup` 註冊並選擇 **Business** 方案。註冊端點尚未上線；在此期間請[申請搶先體驗](https://agent-assembly.com/early-access)。"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:180
msgid "On the **Billing** page, enter your credit card details (processed via Stripe)."
msgstr "在 **Billing** 頁面輸入你的信用卡資料（透過 Stripe 處理）。"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:181
msgid "Complete workspace setup (name, region) as in the Pro flow above."
msgstr "如上方 Pro 流程般完成工作區設定（名稱、地區）。"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:182
msgid "Connect SSO: navigate to **Settings → Authentication → SSO** and follow the [SAML 2.0 or OIDC setup steps](cloud-deployment.md#sso-configuration). SSO is optional at the Business tier but recommended for teams."
msgstr "連接 SSO：前往 **Settings → Authentication → SSO**，並依循 [SAML 2.0 或 OIDC 設定步驟](cloud-deployment.md#sso-configuration)。SSO 在 Business 方案為選用，但建議團隊採用。"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:183
msgid "Invite your team under **Settings → Users** — assign roles (Admin, Developer, Viewer)."
msgstr "在 **Settings → Users** 下邀請你的團隊 — 指派角色（Admin、Developer、Viewer）。"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:184 src/quickstart-saas.md:214
msgid "Instrument agents and create policies as in the Pro flow."
msgstr "如 Pro 流程般為代理裝設檢測並建立政策。"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:188
msgid "Enterprise Tier"
msgstr "Enterprise 方案"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:190
msgid "**Signup**: form-driven via `https://app.agent-assembly.com/contact-sales`."
msgstr "**註冊**：透過 `https://app.agent-assembly.com/contact-sales` 以表單方式進行。"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:192
msgid "**Included features**: unlimited agents, dedicated region (data residency), SCIM provisioning, tamper-evident audit log, audit log retention up to 1 year, 99.9% SLA, 24/7 support (4h response), dedicated SRE contact."
msgstr "**內含功能**：無限代理、專屬地區（資料落地）、SCIM 佈建、防竄改稽核紀錄、稽核紀錄保存最長 1 年、99.9% SLA、全年無休支援（4 小時內回覆）、專屬 SRE 聯絡窗口。"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:194
msgid "**Expected onboarding time**: 1–3 weeks, driven by procurement and security review."
msgstr "**預期上手時間**：1–3 週，取決於採購與安全審查。"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:196
msgid "**Primary contact channel**: your assigned Sales Engineer (SE)."
msgstr "**主要聯絡管道**：你的專屬業務工程師（SE）。"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:198
msgid "Enterprise procurement timeline"
msgstr "Enterprise 採購時程"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:200
msgid "Week"
msgstr "週次"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:200
msgid "Activity"
msgstr "活動"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:202
msgid "**Week 1**"
msgstr ""

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:202
msgid "Submit the `/contact-sales` form → initial SE call (30 min) → receive the Enterprise Order Form and DPA/BAA templates"
msgstr "提交 `/contact-sales` 表單 → 首次 SE 通話（30 分鐘）→ 取得 Enterprise 訂購單與 DPA/BAA 範本"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:203
msgid "**Week 2**"
msgstr ""

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:203
msgid "Legal review of DPA / BAA → IT security review → contract signature"
msgstr "DPA / BAA 法務審查 → IT 安全審查 → 合約簽署"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:204
msgid "**Week 3**"
msgstr ""

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:204
msgid "SE-led workspace provisioning → SSO + SCIM setup with your IdP team → pilot agent onboarding"
msgstr "由 SE 主導的工作區佈建 → 與你的 IdP 團隊進行 SSO + SCIM 設定 → 試行代理上手"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:206
msgid "Enterprise-specific steps"
msgstr "Enterprise 專屬步驟"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:208
msgid "Submit the contact form at `https://app.agent-assembly.com/contact-sales`. Include estimated agent count, primary region preference, and compliance requirements (SOC 2, HIPAA, GDPR)."
msgstr "於 `https://app.agent-assembly.com/contact-sales` 提交聯絡表單。內容包含預估代理數量、偏好的主要地區，以及合規需求（SOC 2、HIPAA、GDPR）。"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:209
msgid "During the SE call, confirm your IdP (Okta, Azure AD, PingFederate, etc.) and data residency requirement."
msgstr "在 SE 通話中，確認你的 IdP（Okta、Azure AD、PingFederate 等）與資料落地需求。"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:210
msgid "After contract signature, the SE provisions your workspace in the selected dedicated region and sends your Workspace ID and initial API key."
msgstr "合約簽署後，SE 會在所選的專屬地區佈建你的工作區，並寄送你的 Workspace ID 與初始 API 金鑰。"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:211
msgid "Configure **SSO** (SAML or OIDC) per [Cloud Deployment → SSO Configuration](cloud-deployment.md#sso-configuration)."
msgstr "依 [Cloud Deployment → SSO Configuration](cloud-deployment.md#sso-configuration) 設定 **SSO**（SAML 或 OIDC）。"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:212
msgid "Configure **SCIM** provisioning per [Cloud Deployment → SCIM User Provisioning](cloud-deployment.md#scim-user-provisioning) for automated user lifecycle management."
msgstr "依 [Cloud Deployment → SCIM User Provisioning](cloud-deployment.md#scim-user-provisioning) 設定 **SCIM** 佈建，以自動化使用者生命週期管理。"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:213
msgid "Configure **budgets** per [Cloud Deployment → Budget Configuration](cloud-deployment.md#budget-configuration) for per-team LLM spend caps."
msgstr "依 [Cloud Deployment → Budget Configuration](cloud-deployment.md#budget-configuration) 設定**預算**，以設定各團隊的 LLM 開銷上限。"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:218
msgid "Next steps"
msgstr "後續步驟"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:220
msgid "[Cloud deployment](cloud-deployment.md) — SSO/SCIM deep-dive, region selection, billing, SLA tiers"
msgstr "[雲端部署](cloud-deployment.md) — SSO/SCIM 深入說明、地區選擇、計費、SLA 方案"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:221
msgid "[Policy reference](policy-reference.md) — full policy rule schema"
msgstr "[政策參考](policy-reference.md) — 完整的政策規則結構描述"

#: src/quickstart-saas.md:222
msgid "[Open core boundary](open-core-boundary.md) — what's in the OSS core vs. the enterprise tier"
msgstr "[開放核心邊界](open-core-boundary.md) — 開源核心與企業方案各含哪些內容"

